WHY CHOOSE THIS PRODUCT


















Guard Against Phishing
Protect your customers with up to 256-bit encryption and 3 algorithms—while providing visual proof that they’re really on your site.





















Encryption and Authentication
Extended Validation gives your customers proof that they can confidently transact with you. And that translates to better business.





















Support: Built Right In
User-friendly tools deliver time-saving automation and management. And if you need help, we're here, 24/7. Free.










Download White Paper    
















Features & Pricing


Our Extended Validation Certificates bring next-generation encryption to Secure Site Pro, along with vulnerability and threat detection for your entire site. All backed by our best-in-class management tools and world-renowned 24/7 customer service.




























Website Scanning


Protection beyond the certificate: With automatic daily malware and website vulnerability scanning, you can proactively protect your sites without taking your eye off the ball.
























Norton Secured Seal


Trust online starts at the Search Results page. With the most recognized trust seal in the world next to your search listing, you have credentials people click on.






























Protection You Can See


Our EV certificates use ECC, the most powerful encryption algorithm in existence. This produces visual cues so visitors know they're with 64,000 times stronger encryption—and full authentication.
























Support Online (And Off)


The Symantec Trust Center gives you visibility and control of your SSL certificates and services. With a single sign-in, you can renew, buy, activate services, access backups and more. And no matter what, we're here to help, 24/7.









































