SSL/TLS Certificates











Recommended For


Internal Networks


Secure Site



Even internal networks and communications should be protected with strong security, malware scanning, and the Norton Secured Seal.











Recommended For


Public Websites


Secure Site w/EV



Two encryption algorithms enhance security, while the green browser bar and Norton Secured Seal build confidence into every interaction.










Recommended For


Public Websites


Secure Site Pro



This certificate secures private connections between browsers and your servers, including gateways, forms, email, and VPNs.










Recommended For


Transactional Websites


Secure Site Pro w/EV



Extended Validation instantly establishes customer trust on sites to ensure privacy and security, even on non-transactional pages











Recommended For


Multi-Domain


Secure Site Wildcard



One SSL Wildcard certificate secures complex websites with multiple domains – effectively and conveniently.








